As [per this discussion](https://github.com/IntuitiveWebSolutions/BriteCore-UI/pull/184#discussion_r171072815), The current `DataTable` implementation mutates the input rows directly any time it needs to keep state on each row (currently, it keeps selection state & row id). 

That approach does work, but is definitely not ideal. This story is for picking a better approach and implementing it.

